cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for solving abstract visual reasoning tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning models and classifiers, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves improving the performance of classifiers, which is a topic studied in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques, which are studied in cs.CL (Computation and Language).
